fr.eikasus.objectsmyfriends.model.bll

Class ManagerFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.eikasus.objectsmyfriends.model.bll.ManagerFactory

  • @ApplicationScoped
public class ManagerFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Class handling object managers.

    This class is used to retrieve a particular object manager, like user, item or image for exemple. Because its instance is passed to each manager after creation, each manager can use other managers.
